Measles case confirmed in Oakland County
------------------------------------
DETROIT: Tests have confirmed that a 15-month-old girl in Oakland County has measles. Health officials think she may have been exposed while traveling in southeast Asia. The child was seen at a local doctor's office on 10 Jan 2012. That office is working with the county's Department of Health to identify any other patients who may have been exposed.

